From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:40:21 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] drm/panthor: Add Sky1 GPU support and ACPI

Add CIX Sky1 GPU support including SCMI perf domain DVFS,
ACE-Lite coherency with NC memattr fallback, RCSU core
harvesting, and ACPI power-on and device frequency scaling.
---
